caption:
Today we had an incredible lunch spread at the new For Five Coffee @forfive in Atlanta! 🥐✨

From the perfectly flaky almond croissant to the savory spanakopita and hearty chicken bowl, every bite was worth the trip. The birria grilled cheese was an unexpected standout, and the peach French toast? Simply divine!

The drinks were on another level - don’t miss their matcha macadamia lavender latte (absolute heaven!), rich Gotham mocha, and refreshing Freddo cappuccino.

Perfect spot for breakfast or lunch with options for every taste. The atmosphere matches the quality of the food - cozy yet stylish.

Have you been to @forfive yet? What’s your go-to order?
